{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-contact-information-and-spelling/task-3","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 3","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Poder</span> je glagol koji se često koristi u zahtevima za poštovanje. Znači imati sposobnost da se nešto uradi.</p>\n<p>Glagoli u španskom menjaju se zavisno od osobe kojoj razgovaraš. Kada pitaš nekoga da li može nešto da uradi, moraš promeniti glavni glagol.</p>\n<p>Recimo da želiš pitati nekoga da li ti može pomoći, možeš reći:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Puedes hablar más despacio?</span> - Možete li da govorite sporije?</p>\n<p>Napomena da <span class=\"highlighted-text\">poder</span> je promenjeno u formu drugog lica jednine (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">tú</span>): <span class=\"highlighted-text\">puedes</span> kada je sledeći glagol u infinitivu. Stoga, standardna struktura je:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Puedes</span> + infinitiv glagol + <span class=\"highlighted-text\">...?</span></p>\n</section>","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušaj audio snimak i dovrši rečenicu ispod.</p>\n</section>","explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>U ovom pitanju, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">puedes</span> je izmenjeni oblik od <span class=\"highlighted-text\">poder</span>, a sledeći glagol je u infinitivu.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Repetir</span> znači ponoviti nešto, što je primenljivo u strukturi:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Puedes</span> + infinitiv + <span class=\"highlighted-text\">...?</span></p>\n</section>","challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"Spanish Curriculum","superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","block":"es-a1-learn-contact-information-and-spelling","lang":"es","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-contact-information-and-spelling/task-3"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>¿Puedes BLANKlo?</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"repetir","feedback":"<p>Ovo je infinitivni glagol koji znači ponoviti neku stvar.</p>"}]},"inputType":null,"tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":{"setup":{"background":"interview-room2.png","characters":[{"character":"Mateo","position":{"x":50,"y":18,"z":1.5},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ES_A1_mateo_camila_phone_number_dialogue.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":15.53,"finishTimestamp":16.68},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Mateo","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Mateo","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":2.15,"dialogue":{"text":"¿Puedes repetirlo?","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Mateo","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":2.65,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"translationPending":false}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/#es-a1-learn-contact-information-and-spelling","dashedName":"task-3","certification":"a1-professional-spanish","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","chapter":"es-a1-chapter-basic-personal-details","module":"es-a1-module-sharing-your-personal-details","block":"es-a1-learn-contact-information-and-spelling","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-contact-information-and-spelling/task-4","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-contact-information-and-spelling/task-2","id":"699e00de1d62e5071643a7b8","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":19,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-contact-information-and-spelling/task-3"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}